      "id": "PopularPost250309",
      "post_content": "Way solid - there's two very important factors about Armillary Sphere that really give it that edge over a 3/5 card, in addition to being accessible to every color (most notably, non-green :P as mentioned by others).  \n  \n(1) It's card advantage - one artifact ==> two lands = +1 card  \n(2) It's on the mana payment plan. Who remembers how sick [Courier's Capsule](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Courier's Capsule) was back in Shards limited?   \n  \nGotta go 4/5 for the ole 'Millary Sphere ",
      "posted_by": "bowlofgumbo",
